eliance on other medicines is not available.</p><p> </p>","Winchester","Steve Brine","233465 ; 233478 ; 233480 ; 233481","2019-03-21T16:14:41.797Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1091047/answer","Biography information for Steve Brine","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1091047/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1091047/answer",,,,,"17","Health and Social Care","Health and Social Care","2019-03-18","Dialysis Machines","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Health and Social Care, what estimate he has made of the number of patients receiving home-based dialysis in place of hospital-based dialysis in each of the past three years.","false","Biography information for Paul Farrelly","Newcastle-under-Lyme","Paul Farrelly","233479"
